# Job Application Assistant

## Prerequisites

- Python 3.11 or newer

## Install

```powershell
python -m venv .venv
.\.venv\Scripts\Activate.ps1
python -m pip install -e .
```

## Run

Use Streamlit directly:

```powershell
streamlit run src/app/main.py
```

Or use the packaged launcher after installation:

```powershell
app
```

Do not use `python src/app/main.py`. This file is a Streamlit entrypoint, not a regular Python script.
